&lt;div class=&quot;skills inner-content&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to articulate complex technical concepts to non-technical audiences and influence senior decision-makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to inspire, mentor and develop high-performing engineering teams, fostering a collaborative and inclusive environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates the ability to anticipate technological trends and proactively shape the technical direction of the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in navigating complex internal and external dynamics, driving consensus and achieving technical and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
