&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dedicated Security Partner to join our team in Singapore, focusing specifically on our growing engagements in the Singapore Public Sector. This is a unique and critical role, designed to strengthen our security posture, deepen our partnerships in the public sector, and ensure successful and secure delivery.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a trusted advisor, bridging the gap between technical delivery and the demanding security requirements of these clients. You will actively participate in the leadership teams for our Singapore Public Sector accounts and you will help to ensure appropriate governance of security on these accounts, navigating the special confidentiality needs that public sector work often entails. You will report to the BISO for APAC and provide regular reporting to the Thoughtworks APAC Security Governance Committee.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Due to the nature of the projects and specific client security clearance, this role requires the successful candidate to be a Singapore Citizen or PR of Singapore&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
