&lt;p&gt;As a Security Partner for Singapore public sector projects, you will provide expert security guidance and leadership for all Thoughtworks accounts and projects within the Singapore public sector portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Governance &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;: Take ownership of establishing and driving a comprehensive security governance framework tailored to the needs of Singapore public sector accounts. This includes defining and operationalizing key security metrics, identifying and tracking emerging risks, and ensuring timely and accurate reporting to the BISO and APAC Security Governance Committee.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Lead and coordinate the response to security incidents, including containment, eradication, recovery, and post-incident analysis. Ensure timely and accurate communication of security incidents to relevant stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Identify, assess, and manage information security risks specific to Singapore public sector projects, proactively developing and implementing mitigation strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Engagement &amp;amp; Partnership&lt;/strong&gt;: Develop strong relationships with key stakeholders within the Singapore public sector, including security teams and relevant agencies, to understand their evolving security requirements and build trust.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compliance &amp;amp; Audit Support&lt;/strong&gt;: Ensure adherence to relevant security policies, standards, and regulatory requirements. Support internal and external audits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Consulting&lt;/strong&gt;: Provide technical security consulting to delivery teams, embedding security best practices, architectural patterns, and compliance throughout the SDLC. Actively participate in problem-solving by providing timely and effective security solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enable Knowledge Sharing&lt;/strong&gt;: Drive the scalable enablement of Security Champions within delivery teams, empowering them to embed security best practices into their day-to-day work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
